; Reverses the value at 0x3050 into 0x3051.
; CSC 225, Assignment 2
; Given code, Winter '20

0011 0000 0000 0000     ; Start at 0x3000.
0101 000 000 1 00000    ; Clear R0
0001 000 000 1 00001    ; Increment R0.
0101 010 010 1 00000    ; Clear R2
0010 001 001001100      ; Load 0x3050 into R1.
0000 011 000000001      ; Skip next step if positive or zero
0001 010 010 000 000    ; Increment R2 by R0.
0001 000 000 000 000    ; Double R0
0000 010 000000010      ; Skip next two steps if zero
0001 001 001 000 001    ; Double R1
0000 111 111111010      ; Go back six steps
0011 010 001000110      ; Store R1 at 0x3050.
1111 0000 00100101      ; Halt.01010000